Controversial singer Willy Paul aka Pozze has cut his signature dreadlocks. Pozze posted a video of himself in a barbershop with his friend asking him if he had decided to cut off his hair. "Chop it off, chop it off... kwani unaogoapa? Chop it all off." Willy Paul's friend is heard telling the barber in the background. "They're gone man..." Pozze said as he ended the video. Willy Paul did not reveal the reason why he opted to shave his dreads. Recently, content creator Thee Pluto told his fans that he had been promised Sh1 million for the big shave by Nairobi politician Wangui Nganga. In a Q and A session, Thee Pluto saidÂ multiple factors influenced his decision to shave but the financial reward was the deciding factor.